| X64-01 platform + x64 exe | Yes (04+05+06), props Release gap |
| X64-04 deps resolve x64 | Yes (01 LIFT + 04 build-from-source + 06 staging) |
| X64-02 gl05/06/07 char-select | Yes (06-T2), matrix A/B under-specified for 6/7 |
| SC#4 Win32 non-regression | Yes (06-T3, OutDir isolation) |

**Bottom line:** Execute after tightening **depends_on**, **x64-platform.props Configuration split**, **surface census (4 not 8)**, **three-renderer matrix validation**, and **Miles/tinyxml link acceptance**. Do not treat ROADMAP 32-02 unchecked as a code blocker — treat **`D3DXAssembleShader` at `:760`** and **missing `x64-platform.props`** as the live preconditions.
